{"tid":721700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(美國) 白人闖報館「槍擊」多名職員，自殘指紋以隱藏身份","createTime":"2018-06-29T00:46:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T01:09:06.000Z","uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1a7f1427fec5ac009d0df4e149361fe85c4a529c","tid":721700,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T00:46:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=1016445\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_367%26itemid%3D1016445&d=IhhpZRtuF5vgy5gBgPYU3EkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=f0d6d226\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=1016445</a><br />\n<br />\n美國報館槍擊案1名白人男子被捕<br />\n29.06.2018 07:46<br />\n<br />\n美國馬里蘭州1間報館發生槍擊案，5人死亡，多人重傷。警方在現場拘捕1名持有長槍的白人男子，消息指他自殘手指，以免透過指紋被認出身份，當局最後利用面容辨識技術，確定疑兇身份，暫時未知他的動機。有執法人員說，目前無跡象指案件涉及恐怖主義。<br />\n<br />\n事發在當地星期四下午2時許，報館內1名記者說，槍手隔著玻璃門開槍，多人中槍，報館內其他人立即躲在枱底，並聽到槍手再上子彈的聲音。"},{"pid":"72ec023b776d73418c0fcd87f1f1355093f65259","tid":721700,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T00:47:31.000Z","msg":"間報館係左傾定右傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f65f11fab578620ccdb36656c4961fede55b18b","tid":721700,"uid":59283,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T00:47:50.000Z","msg":"留名睇tbb瘋狂報導"},{"pid":"7b02bfe616d823be487be2d869f3b34de3b39eec","tid":721700,"uid":30510,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T00:51:27.000Z","msg":"黑人會唔會係標題到提？<br />\nRacist"},{"pid":"c501fe348669f043843cb22f1e4dfb886911323a","tid":721700,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72ec023b776d73418c0fcd87f1f1355093f65259","tid":721700,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T00:47:31.000Z","msg":"間報館係左傾定右傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgm